                              automata.scm

Implementation of Deterministic Finite Automata (DFAs) on r7rs scheme.

The file ./automata.scm contains the implementation of the procedures to
make a DFA (make-dfa) and run it on a string (dfa-run).

The file ./exempla.scm contains examples of DFAs implemented using the
procedures of the other file.  This is an executable file; when run, it
computes those DFAs on a set of strings.

